reviewText: The title is misspelled on all inserts and the dvd--Witcraft, instead of Witchcraft. That makes it seem like less reliable information.
many good point of view of different times and action taken to witches

This video is the same as A&E ancient mysteries withes with leonard nemoy,except with a different narrator. I took the time to look at the product numbers and running time and release date to make sure I did not get the video I already owned, but its the same. The video is good and informative. But I feel like they pulled a fast one on me and I wasted $30. They put it out there as a different product, shame on ya'll.
